cap: And when I could find work loading the ships, I would eat.

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: If not, I dreamed of food.

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: Today, I am the richest man in Qarth.

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: Do you think the path from poverty to wealth is always pure and honourable?

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: I have done many things, Khaleesi, that a righteous man would condemn.

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: And here I am, with no regrets.

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: Bar the gates. Ring the bells.

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: Slowly, Khaleesi.

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: Where are they?

name: The Old Gods and the New
cap: Where are my dragons?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A cripple?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You let a cripple escape?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The boy can't walk, but somehow he slipped past you?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The giant must have took him.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The giant?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Hodor?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Oh, that's all right, then.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You let a halfwit escape with a cripple.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And Rickon, too? The little one?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Gone, along with the wildling woman.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The one you were fucking.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Right.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Get the horses and the hounds.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Come on, find the scent.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Where they going?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Halt!

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Enjoying your first hunt?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: So far, hunting seems very similar to riding, my lord.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: With hunting, there's blood at the end.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They're little boys.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I was a little boy when I was torn away from my home and brought here.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: So I kept my word. I never ran away.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If I find them soon enough, I won't hurt them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Well, I'll hurt them, but I won't kill them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Those boys are of far more value to you alive than dead.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They have no value to me missing.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Robb will have sent a force to retake Winterfell by now.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Robb's in the Riverlands. My sister's in Deepwood Motte.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She'll get here long before they do.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And Ned Stark always said 500 men could hold Winterfell against 10,000.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We have a scent!

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The hounds have the scent.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Come, Maester, don't look so grim.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It's all just a game.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We should have took more food.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We couldn't risk going to the kitchens.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Those people all love you. They would have given you whatever you needed.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And if Theon found out, he'd hang them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The boy can't survive on walnuts. - I'm fine.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We've been walking since before sunrise.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Even Hodor will tire. - Hodor.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Even you, sweet giant. - Hodor.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Wait, I know that farm.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I sent those two Winterfell orphans there.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Jack and Billy.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They'll give us some food. - We can't risk it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If Theon tracks us here, he'll torture them until he finds out where we are.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Billy climbs a tree better than anyone.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You've never seen me climb a tree, little man.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They'll be after us with hounds.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We got a good start on them, but we can't outrun hounds forever.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Did you pull a knife on me in the night?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: What's the matter?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Can't be the first time you pressed your bone against a woman's arse.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Let's move.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It is the first time.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: How old are you, boy?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'm a man of the Night's Watch.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You're a boy who's never been with a girl.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Don't your stones start to hurt if your bone never gets...

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Don't call them that.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: What, stones?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Or bone?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Neither.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Both.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Move!

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I heard they get all swollen and bruised if you don't use them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Of course, maybe that's just what the lads say when they want me feeling sorry for them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: As if I'd feel sorry for them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Are there no girl crows?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: There are no women of the Night's Watch, no.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: So the lads just do it with each other?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: No.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Never? - Never.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We swore an oath.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You have sheep at the Wall?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: With your hands, then?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: No wonder you're all so miserable.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Would you please shut up? - Would you please shut up?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You think you're better than me, crow.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'm a free woman. - You're a free woman?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I might be your prisoner, but I'm a free woman.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If you're my prisoner, you're not a free woman. That's what 'prisoner' means.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And you think you're free?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You swore some stupid oath and now you can never touch a girl.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It was my choice to say the words.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: So you don't like girls? - Of course I like girls.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: But you chose never to touch them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: That's the price you pay if you want to be a man of the Night's Watch.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: So instead of getting naked with a girl, you'd prefer to invade our lands...

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Invade your lands?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Wildlings raid our lands all the time.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Some of them tried to kill my little brother, a crippled boy!

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They're not your lands!

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We've been here the whole time.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You lot came along and just put up a big wall and said it was yours.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: My father was Ned Stark.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I have the blood of the First Men.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: My ancestors lived here, same as yours.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: So why are you fighting us?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Go on.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Now I want you to tell me what happened.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Come on, this way.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Come on, speak up. Speak up.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Wolfsbane.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A rare substance.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: This is no common assassin.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We hanged 20 men last night.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I don't care if you hanged 100.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A man tried to kill me. I want his name and I want his head.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We think it was an infiltrator from the Brotherhood Without Banners.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Pretentious name for a band of outlaws.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We can't allow rebels behind our lines to harass us with impunity.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We look like fools and they look like heroes. That's how kings fall.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I want them dead, every one.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Killing them isn't the problem.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It's finding them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Have you gone soft, Clegane?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I always thought you had a talent for violence.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Burn the villages, burn the farms.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Let them know what it means to choose the wrong side.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Mmm.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Is that mutton?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Yes, my lord.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Don't like mutton.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'll bring something else. - Leave it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Are you hungry? - No.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Of course you are.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Eat.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'll eat in the kitchen later.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It's bad manners to refuse a lord's offer.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Sit.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Eat.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You're small for your age.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I suppose you've been underfed your whole life.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I eat a lot.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I just don't grow.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Mmm.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: This will be my last war.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Win or lose.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Have you ever lost before?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Do you think I'd be in my position if I had lost a war?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: But this is the one I'll be remembered for.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The War of Five Kings, they're calling it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: My legacy will be determined in the coming months.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Do you know what legacy means?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It's what you pass down to your children and your children's children.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It's what remains of you when you're gone.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Harren the Black thought this castle would be his legacy.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The greatest fortress ever built.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The tallest towers, the strongest walls.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The Great Hall had 35 hearths.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Thirty-five. Can you imagine?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Look at it now.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A blasted ruin.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Do you know what happened?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Dragons?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Yes.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Dragons happened.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Harrenhal was built to withstand an attack from the land.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A million men could have marched on these walls,

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: and a million men would have been repelled.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: But an attack from the air with dragon fire... Mmm-mmm.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Harren and all his sons roasted alive within these walls.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Aegon Targaryen changed the rules.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: That's why every child alive still knows his name

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: 300 years after his death.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Aegon and his sisters.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Mmm?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It wasn't just Aegon riding his dragon.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It was Rhaenys and Visenya, too.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Correct.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A student of history, are you?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Rhaenys rode Meraxes.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Visenya rode Vhagar.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'm sure I knew that when I was a boy.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Visenya Targaryen was a great warrior.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She had a Valyrian steel sword she called Dark Sister.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Hmm.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She's a heroine of yours, I take it?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Aren't most girls more interested in the pretty maidens from the songs?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Jonquil with the flowers in her hair?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Most girls are idiots.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You remind me of my daughter.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Where did you learn all this stuff about Visenya and her Valyrian steel sword?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: From my father.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: He was a well-read stonemason.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Can't say I've ever met a literate stonemason.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Have you met many stonemasons, my lord?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Careful now, girl.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I enjoy you, but be careful.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Take that back to the kitchen.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Eat what you want.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And, girl.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: 'M'lord.'

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Lowborn girls say 'm'lord,'

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: not 'my lord.'

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If you're going to pose as a commoner, you should do it properly.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: My mother served Lady Dustin for many years, my lord.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She taught me how to speak proper... Properly.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You're too smart for your own good. Has anyone told you that?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Yes.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Go on.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I beg pardon, ser.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I should have come to you after to thank you for saving me.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You were so brave. - Brave?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A dog doesn't need courage to chase off rats.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Does it give you joy to scare people?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: No, it gives me joy to kill people.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Spare me. You can't tell me

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Lord Eddard Stark of Winterfell never killed a man.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It was his duty. He never liked it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Is that what he told you?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: He lied.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Killing is the sweetest thing there is.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Why are you always so hateful?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You'll be glad of the hateful things I do someday when you're queen

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: and I'm all that stands between you and your beloved king.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I've demanded a meeting of the Thirteen. One of them did this or knows who did.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You are one of the Thirteen.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If I wanted your dragons, I would have taken them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They mean nothing to me on their own. - Nothing?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They're more valuable than anything in the world.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Shall we look inside my vault

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: and see what selling your dragons would buy me I cannot buy already?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We will get them back.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: There is no we, so why would you help me get them back?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I took you under my protection in front of the rulers of my city.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A man is what others say he is and no more.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If they say that Xaro Xhoan Daxos is a liar, my word is worth nothing.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I cannot let this thing happen to you under my roof.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: But it did happen under your roof.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Khaleesi, many times in my life, I have been...

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I don't care where you've been.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You think we're savages because we don't live in stone castles.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We can't make steel as good as yours, it's true, but...

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We're free.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If someone tried to tell us we couldn't lie down as man and woman,

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: we'd shove a spear up his arse.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We don't go serving some shit king who's only king because his father was.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: No.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: No, you serve Mance Rayder, the King beyond the Wall.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We chose Mance Rayder to lead us.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: He was a crow, same as you, but he wanted to be free.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You could be free, too.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You don't need to live your whole life taking commands from old men.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Wake up when you want to wake up.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I could show you the streams to fish, the woods to hunt.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Build yourself a cabin and find a woman to lie with in the night.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You're a pretty lad.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The girls would claw each other's eyes out to get naked with you.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Walk.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I could teach you how to do it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I know how to do it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You know nothing, Jon Snow.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And what did she say?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She admired your spirit, Your Grace.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And what then?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She...

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If every man were held accountable for the actions of every distant relative, Ser Alton,

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: we'd all hang.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She tore the paper in half, Your Grace.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You've acted with honour.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I thank you for it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Lord Karstark, see that Ser Alton's pen is clean, and give him a hot supper.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Ser Alton's pen is occupied, Your Grace.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The prisoners from the Yellow Fork.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Too many prisoners.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Is there room for Ser Alton?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Does he need to lie down?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Have the men build him a new pen.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Put him in with the Kingslayer for now.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Have your boy watch over them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Torrhen.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: That will be all.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Your Grace.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: A minute of your time?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I've been treating your wounded men.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And my enemies, as some of my bannermen are fond of mentioning.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They're not my enemies.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: That's what I tell my bannermen.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I've already run through the supplies I brought with me.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Some are easily replaced. Egg yolks, turpentine, oil of roses.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: But some are not.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I need silk for stitching.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I need fennel root for those with fever, willow bark. Mostly I need milk of the poppy.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You saw what it was like to amputate a foot without any.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I assume there will be more loss of limb before this war is over.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If you need help finding these... - I know where to find them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'm sorry, I shouldn't interrupt you.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Continue, my lady.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You're riding to the Crag to negotiate a surrender?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Yes.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The Crag will have a maester and he will have what I need.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I expect he will.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: If I could write a list.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Come with me to the Crag.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I don't think that will be...

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Let the maester show you his stores.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I want the wounded men to be treated well,

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: all the wounded men.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Children, come inside, quick. - Come on.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Hurry up!

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Can't find anything, ser.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They've lost the scent. - Try again.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We've circled this farmhouse twice. There's no sign of them.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We could start the search fresh in the morning, my lord.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'm looking at spending the rest of my life

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: being treated like a fool and a eunuch by my own people.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Ask yourself, is there anything I wouldn't do to stop that from happening?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The hounds will find the scent again. I'll beat them until they do.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I'll whip every man here until I have both those boys in hand.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And once I've got them, the pampered little shits...

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: It's better to be cruel than weak.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Prince Theon.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Where are they? - Who, m'lord?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The Stark boys. Where are they?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I don't know. I seen no one.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Think harder.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I swear, m'lord. I don't know.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: My lord, over here.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I think I've found what we're looking for.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Send the old man home.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Go back to Winterfell.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Take him back.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Theon, don't do this.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You came back. - As soon as I heard.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Do you know anything?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Irri is dead. - I know.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She was a good... - She's dead.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She died alone. She died for me and I couldn't protect her.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Doreah?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We can't find her.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: She must be dead, too.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I led my people out of the Red Waste and into the slaughterhouse.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I should have been here.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You went to find me a ship.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: My place is by your side.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I shouldn't have left you alone with these people.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: 'These people'?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They are not to be trusted.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And who is to be trusted?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Who are my people?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The Targaryens?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I only knew one, my brother,

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: and he would have let a thousand men rape me if it had got him the crown.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The Dothraki?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Most of them turned on me the day that Khal Drogo fell from his horse.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Your people are in Westeros.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: The people in Westeros don't know I'm alive.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They will soon enough. - And then what?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They'll pray for my return?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: They'll wave dragon banners and shout my name?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: That's what my brother believed and he was a fool.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You are not your brother.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Trust me, Khaleesi.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: There it is.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: 'Trust me.'

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: And it's you I should trust, Ser Jorah?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Only you?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I don't need trust any longer.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: I don't want it and I don't have room for it.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: You are too young to be so... - And you are too familiar.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Forgive me, Khaleesi.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: No one can survive in this world without help. No one.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Let me help you, please.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Tell me how.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: Find my dragons.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: How long till we get back to your crows?

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: We're close.

name: A Man Without Honor
cap: What, a day? A half-day?

name: A Man Without Honor

cap: Yes, he had that reputation. And they named him traitor and took his head.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Joffrey.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Joffrey did that.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He promised he would be merciful

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: and he cut my father's head off.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And he said that was mercy.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Then he took me up on the walls and made me look at it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Go on.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I can't. I never meant...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My father was a traitor.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My brother as well. I have traitor's blood.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Please don't make me say any more.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: She's terrified, Grandmother. Look at her.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Speak freely, child.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We would never betray your confidence, I swear it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He's a monster.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Ah.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That's a pity.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Please, don't stop the wedding.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Have no fear. The Lord Oaf of Highgarden

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: is determined that Margaery shall be queen.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Even so, we thank you for the truth.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Ah.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Here comes my cheese.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We're at war. This march is a distraction.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My grandfather's funeral is not a distraction.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Are we riding to battle at Riverrun?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Then it's a distraction.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My Uncle Edmure has his forces garrisoned there.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We need his men.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Unless he's been breeding them,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: he don't have enough to make a difference.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Have you lost faith in our cause?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: If it's revenge, I still got faith in it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: If you no longer believe...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I can believe till it snows in Dorne.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Don't change the fact that we've got half the men.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You don't think we can win?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: May I speak my mind, Your Grace?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Have you not been speaking your mind, Lord Karstark?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I think you lost this war the day you married her.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Whoa! Whoa!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Your Grace.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You're afraid of her.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And she knows it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm not afraid of her.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: May I help you, Lady Stark?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm sorry, I shouldn't have...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You can't help because a mother

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: makes one for her children to protect them.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Only a mother can make them.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You've made them before?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Twice.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Did they work?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: After a fashion.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I prayed for my son Bran to survive his fall.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Many years before that, one of the boys came down with the pox.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Maester Luwin said if he made it through the night, he'd live.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But it would be a very long night.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: So I sat with him all through the darkness.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Listened to his ragged little breaths.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: His coughing, his whimpering.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Which boy?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Jon Snow.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: When my husband brought that baby home from the war, I couldn't bear to look at him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I didn't want to see those brown

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: stranger's eyes staring up at me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: So I prayed to the Gods, take him away. Make him die.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He got the pox.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And I knew I was the worst woman who ever lived.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A murderer.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'd condemned this poor, innocent child to a horrible death

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: all because I was jealous of his mother.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A woman he didn't even know.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: So I prayed to all seven Gods,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: let the boy live.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Let him live and I'll love him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'll be a mother to him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'll beg my husband to give him a true name,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: to call him Stark and be done with it,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: to make him one of us.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And he lived.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And he lived.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And I couldn't keep my promise.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And everything that's happened since then,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: all this horror that's come to my family,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: it's all because I couldn't love a motherless child.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Was it hard for you to kill the Halfhand?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You liked him?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I like you, but if you're playing us false,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: it won't be hard for me to kill you.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I've got wildling blood in my veins. These are my people.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I understand.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Well, how could you understand?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You want to protect your people.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Do you know what it takes to unite 90 clans,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: half of whom want to massacre the other half for one insult or another?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: They speak seven different languages in my army.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The Thenns hate the Hornfoots. The Hornfoots hate the ice-river clans.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Everyone hates the cave people.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: So you know how I got moon worshippers and cannibals and giants

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: to march together in the same army?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I told them we were all going to die if we don't get south.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Because that's the truth.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Shouldn't be long now.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What's wrong with him?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He's a warg.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He can enter the mind of animals, see through their eyes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He's scouting for us.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What, you've never met a warg?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Orell.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Where were you this time?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The Fist of the First Men.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What did you see?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Dead crows.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What's the matter, Piggy? You crying 'cause you're cold?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: There's 200 brothers killed by dead men

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: and you're still here

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: whimpering.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That seem fair to you?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I seen 'em torn to pieces fighting while you was off somewhere hiding in a hole.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why don't you lie down and rest for a while, eh?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You know you want to.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Hey.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Get up, Sam.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Get up.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I can't.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: If you stop, you'll die.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: 'Course if you don't stop, you'll probably die, too.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You don't care.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: 'Course we care.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You left me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: When the White Walkers came, you left me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Aye, we left you. You're fat and you're slow.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We didn't want to die.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Help me get him up.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Looks like that piggy is done for.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Help us get him up.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He's slowing us down.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Just get him up!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why? So the rest of us can die?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We'll move faster without him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What is this? Get up, Tarly.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Is he all right?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Aye, I think so.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We may as well just go without him. - That's enough.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Tarly, I forbid you to die.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Do you hear me?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why should the rest of us...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Rast, you're responsible for him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What am I supposed to do?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Make sure he gets back alive.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: If he doesn't, you don't.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Move on!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm not dying for you, Piggy. You hear me?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Where's Rickon and Hodor?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Looking for food.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What's out there?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Not another step, boy. Unless you want to drown in your own blood.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm unarmed.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That was poor planning.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My sister carries the weapons.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm better with them.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Drop the spear.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Drop it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: If you kill me, that wolf will tear you to bits.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You must be Summer.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm Jojen Reed. This is my sister, Meera.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We've come a long way to find you, Brandon.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And we have much farther to go.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm just trying to understand.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Would you please shut up about it?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Jaqen H'ghar offered you three kills.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm not listening.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But just explain it to me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He offered to kill any three people you wanted. Dead.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: All you had to do was give him the names. Anyone.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You could have picked King Joffrey.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Shut up.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You could have picked Tywin Lannister.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Jaqen got us out of Harrenhal, so why are you complaining?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But you could have ended the war.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Where are we going?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: North.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We should have come to the Red Fork River by now.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Maybe we passed it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's 100 feet wide. How could we have passed it?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: If we hit the Red Fork, we can follow it west to Riverrun.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My mother grew up there. My grandfather's a lord. He'll protect us.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Could be a minstrel. - Shut up.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A minstrel's got gold sometimes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We could jump him, tie him up, steal his gold, and buy some food.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Shh!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And so he spoke, and so he spoke

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That lord of Castamere

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But now the rains weep o'er his hall

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: With no one there to hear

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What's lurking behind that wall? A lion? A wolf?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Just a dirty little cub, I think.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Loose a few more shafts. - Don't.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Put the sword down, girl.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You go on down the road. Keep singing so we know where you are.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Leave us be and I won't kill you.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Generous.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You're a dangerous person.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I like dangerous people.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why are your friends so shy?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What friends?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The fat one to your left and the lad beside him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Three young ones on the run carrying castle-forged swords.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You escape from Harrenhal?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Who are you?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Thoros of Myr.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The fellow with the bow is Anguy.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No, who do you fight for?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The Brotherhood Without Banners.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Now come along.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I want to hear how two boys and a very dangerous girl escaped Harrenhal.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm not going with them. The Brotherhood?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That's who the Mountain were looking for.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: They'll bring us back and put rats in us.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You've got nothing to fear from us.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The lords of Westeros want to burn the countryside.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We're trying to save it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Now come on. We'll talk more over brown bread and stew.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And then you can go on your way.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Here's the thing, fat boy.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: When I'm done talking, that arrow's falling down on your fat head.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: So I advise you move, because I'm done talking.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Half the country's starving and look at this one.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Maybe he's the reason half the country's starving.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My lion.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We've spoken of this.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You cannot come here.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But you said I should come to you with any problems.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Did anyone see you?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No. - You sure?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My father does not make idle threats.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Having you killed would be the high point of his week.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You have to be absolutely certain.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: All right. What is this problem?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm worried about Sansa.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: When she spoke with Lord Baelish,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: his friend warned me about him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Baelish doesn't have friends.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I don't know her name.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Oh, Ros? The redhead?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: How do you know her?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I try to know as many people as I can.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You never know which one you'll need.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: She's a whore.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yes, well, we shouldn't be judgemental about these things.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You fucked her.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Oh, please.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: All right, yes, I fucked her once.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Twice.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But since I met you, my lady, I've been with no one else.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And was she good? Did you like her?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Not as much as I like you, obviously,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: or she'd be the one torturing me right now.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What did she say about Littlefinger?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That Sansa shouldn't trust him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Is there an idiot in any village who trusts Littlefinger?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We have to protect her.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We can't.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Now that the Lannisters have discarded her, Sansa will have many suitors.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A great beauty with a very old name.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A great beauty? Oh, a great beauty?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yes, she is, objectively, very.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Her face is quite pleasing, to other men and to women,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: people in general.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But not to me, of course.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I only have eyes for you.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You pervert. You want her?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: This child?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I don't even want to talk about her.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But you are.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Only because you're making me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I didn't force you to open

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: your mouth and make words come out.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: This is cruel and unfair. Cruelly unfair.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Aw! 'The cruelty. Shae is so cruel to me.'

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Mmm. Yes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Now do you think I'm cruel?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Only if you stop.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But you mustn't come here again.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Do you hear me?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You've come to a dangerous place full of dangerous people.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Dangerous people. Mmm.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Lady Tyrell, my king.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Send her in.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You wanted to see me, Your Grace?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm leaving on a hunting trip.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I just wanted to make sure you had everything you need before I left.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That's very thoughtful, Your Grace.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I have everything I could want.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Good. Good.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: How are you finding life in the capital?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It must be quite a change after Renly's camp.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A welcome one.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A military encampment is no place for a lady.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And the bedside of a traitor?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Is that a place for a lady?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Your Grace,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I tried to do my duty as a wife, that is all.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What was your duty to this traitor as you saw it?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The duty of any wife to any husband. To provide him with children.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You failed to do this.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why? - I...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I would not speak ill of the dead.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You think one ought to speak kindly of a traitor

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: 'cause he had a sword put through his heart?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No. I do beg your pardon.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The subtleties of politics are often lost on me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Renly...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I don't believe he was interested in the company of women.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What makes you say this?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Whenever I wanted to make a child with him, he...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He had so many excuses, so many late-night war councils.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He never wanted to try.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Except one evening,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: after he'd had far too much wine to drink, he suggested something...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Something that sounded very painful

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: and couldn't possibly result in children.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Maybe the fault was with me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No, he was a known degenerate.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's such a relief to hear you say so, Your Grace.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Mmm.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I've considered making his perversion punishable by death.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: As is your right.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You must do whatever you need to do.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You are the king.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I am.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Do you like it?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I just had it made. Probably one of

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: the finest weapons in the Seven Kingdoms.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's beautiful. Will you show me how it works?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's a new design. Much easier to load. There's no crank.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You use this lever to draw the string.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The bolt goes here.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And then you just aim...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Would you take me hunting sometime?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Forgive me, Your Grace. I know a hunt is no place for a woman.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's not unheard of.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: My father would never let me before...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You no longer belong to him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Do you want to hold it?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: May I? Please.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I imagine it must be so exciting to squeeze your finger here

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: and watch something die over there.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Could you do it?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Could you kill something?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I don't know, Your Grace. Do you think I could?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Would you like to watch me?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Stop! Stop!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Tell us the truth.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: About what?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I don't know what you want.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I want the truth.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What truth?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why'd you take Winterfell?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I took it to... I took it...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Who gave the orders? - No one.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I took it on my own. - Why?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: To take the North while vulnerable.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: And once you took it?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Hold it. Rule it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Good. That's very good.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why did you do that? I told you.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Why did you take Winterfell?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I took it to bring glory to my house and my father.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Wait. Wait, wait, wait. I took it because I hated the Starks.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I hated them for holding me prisoner. I wanted to hurt them.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What are you doing?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Please.

cap: I'll tell you anything. Just take it off.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Please. Please, just take it off.

cap: Your sister sent me. - Yara?

cap: I'll come for you tonight when the castle sleeps.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: No, don't go. Please, please. No, please don't leave me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Please, please. Please, please don't go!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Please. Please. Don't leave me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Please don't go.

cap: Rickon, stay with us.

cap: It's all right. The wolves will protect him.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You can get inside his head, see through his eyes.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Only when I'm asleep.

cap: That's how it begins until you learn to control it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You're a warg.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's not just wolves. Sometimes in my dreams there's a...

cap: A three-eyed raven?

cap: You've seen it?

cap: We saw him together. You haven't forgotten?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Does it have anything to do with warging?

cap: No, the raven is something different, something deeper.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Seeing things that haven't happened yet?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Or things that happened long before you were born

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: or things that are happening right now thousands of miles away.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What's he telling him?

cap: Why don't you ask?

cap: Isn't he ashamed, your brother, needing you to protect him?

cap: Where's the shame in that?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Any boy his age who needs his sister to protect him

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: is gonna find himself needing lots of protecting.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Some people will always need help.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That doesn't mean they're not worth helping.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: When my father died, I dreamt it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You didn't dream it. You saw it. So did I.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You have the sight, too?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: When I told my father about your father,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: for the first time in my life, I saw him cry.

cap: Your father is Howland Reed?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yeah.

cap: He saved my father's life during the rebellion.

cap: Your father told you about the rebellion?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Mine never did. But I saw that, too.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What else have you seen?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Only one thing that matters,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: you.

cap: I never liked the skinny ones. Like drinking from a puddle.

cap: Not that I'm averse to drinking from a puddle every now and again.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I don't drink ale.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: There's no story so good a drink won't make it better.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yeah! - You see?

cap: They've suffered through my bouts of

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: sobriety. It's very tedious for all concerned.

cap: Now, how did three children...

cap: We're not children.

cap: How did three young persons such as yourselves,

cap: Gendry's a smith. He was apprenticed in the armoury.

cap: King's Landing. Tobho Mott's shop.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That criminal. He charges twice as much

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: as every other armourer in the city.

cap: That's because he's twice as good. - Ah-ha!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A smith and a salesman.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Gendry stole us weapons. - Ah!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Fought your way out of Harrenhal, I see.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: He knows how to use a sword and so do I.

cap: My brothers taught me.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Ooh!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: To your brothers!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You can finish your meals before you go.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It may be awhile before you see another.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You'll free us?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I gave you my word.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But before you go,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: allow me to raise a cup to your...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Hey, hey.

cap: Now that is an uncommonly large person.

cap: How does one manage to subdue such an uncommonly large person?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: One waits for him to drink until he passes out.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Poor man. You have my sympathy.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Aha!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Not a man at all.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A Hound!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: So good to see you again, Clegane.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Thoros?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The fuck you doing here?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Drinking and talking too much. Same as ever.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: A pretty prize, lads.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Yeah!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Girl.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What in seven hells are you doing with the Stark bitch?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's a tough decision.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Take the bridge and risk being seen or cross the great water.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Silence.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Anyone can see us on the bridge,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: but cross by water and the current could take us.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Or I could escape down the river.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Good luck.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: It's wonderful to watch you wrestle with these dilemmas.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Which will she choose?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Gambler at heart. Wouldn't have guessed.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Be quick about it.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Oh, I need to rest. - Get up.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I have these, on your feet when you walk too far.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: What do you call them? - Get up now.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Corns. I never used to get corns.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I used to ride everywhere, not march around like a common foot soldier

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: wearing the same shit boots for over a year.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: This heel is ruined. There's no way...

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I never understood why some knights

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: felt the need to carry two swords.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Ooh!

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You move well

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: for a great beast of a woman.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You shouldn't grimace before you lunge. It gives away the game.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Bit of a quandary for you. If you kill me, you fail Lady Stark.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: But if you don't kill me,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I'm going to kill you.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You're good. Graceless, but good.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: See? If you were willing to hurt me, you might have had me there.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Looks like your woman's getting the better of you,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: if you can call that a woman.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: We enjoy a good fight. Gets our juices flowing.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: The Flayed Man of House Bolton. A bit gruesome for my taste.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: You sure he's the one?

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: That's him, all right.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: I saw him fight at the tourney for Ser Willem Frey's wedding.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Give the man his silver.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Let us go and my father will pay you whatever you want.

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words
cap: Enough to buy me a new head?

cap: If the King in the North hears I let the Kingslayer go,

name: Dark Wings, Dark Words

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: If I may, nephew,

cap: I encountered a situation with one of my lieutenants

name: Walk of Punishment

cap: Why don't you shut your mouth about that damned mill?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I wouldn't let you wave your blunders around like a victory flag.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: My blunder sent Tywin's mad dog

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: back to Casterly Rock with his tail between his legs.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I think King Robb understands we won't win this war

cap: if he's the only one winning any battles.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: No, there's glory enough to go around.

name: Walk of Punishment

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Your instructions were to wait for him to come to you.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I seized an opportunity.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: What value was the mill?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: The Mountain was garrisoned across the river from it.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Is he there now?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Of course not. We took the fight to him. He could not withstand us.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I wanted to draw the Mountain into the west,

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: into our country, where we could surround him and kill him.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I wanted him to chase us,

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: which he would have done because he is a mad dog

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: without a strategic thought in his head.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I could have that head on a spike by now.

name: Walk of Punishment

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: We took hostages. Willem Lannister. Martyn Lannister.

cap: Tywin Lannister has my sisters.

cap: Have I sued for peace?

cap: No.

cap: How many men did you lose?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: 208. But for every man we lost, the Lannisters...

cap: We need our men more than Tywin needs his!

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I'm sorry.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I didn't know.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: You would have.

cap: Right here today at this gathering, if you had been patient.

cap: You know who isn't?

cap: Tywin Lannister.

cap: Intimate. Lovely table.

cap: Better chairs than the old Small Council chamber.

cap: What news of Jaime?

cap: You control more spies and informants

cap: Do you mean to tell me that none of you has any notion of where he is?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: We are trying, my lord.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Try harder.

cap: What do we have, then?

cap: Robb Stark and most of his bannermen are in Riverrun

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: for the funeral of his grandfather Lord Hoster Tully.

cap: In Stark's absence, Roose Bolton holds Harrenhal,

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: in practice, not in name.

cap: Let him have it.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: The Lord of Harrenhal will make

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: a worthy suitor for the widow Arryn.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: For which I am extremely grateful to you, my lord.

cap: Lady Arryn and I have known each other since we were children.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: A successful courtship would make

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Lord Baelish acting Lord of the Vale.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Titles do seem to breed titles.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: You'll leave for the Eyrie as soon as possible

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: and bring Lysa Arryn into the fold.

cap: to the list of people who have taken up arms against him.

cap: The royal wedding may end up being

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: the most expensive event in living memory.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Summer has ended, hard days lie ahead.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Not a good time to leave the crown's finances unattended.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Fully agreed.

cap: Which is why I'm naming you new Master of Coin.

cap: Master of Coin?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: It would appear to best suits your talents.

cap: I'm quite good at spending money,

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: but a lifetime of outrageous wealth

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: hasn't taught me much about managing it.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I have no doubt you will prove equal to this challenge.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Hear, hear.

cap: I'm the prisoner of value, not you.

cap: You'd let them do what they wanted?

cap: Why are you helping him?

cap: Better than anyone you've met.

cap: What are you doing? We're about to leave.

cap: Yeah.

cap: You don't burn your fingers.

cap: Good-bye, Hot Pie.

cap: Good-bye, Arry.

cap: Up you go, little lady.

cap: Hey, Hot Pie.

cap: It's really good.

cap: A person could almost be forgiven for forgetting we're at war.

cap: It often comforts me to think that even in war's darkest days,

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: in most places in the world absolutely nothing is happening.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I've missed you, Uncle.

cap: Father missed you, too, from the day you left.

cap: Maybe he never said it in so many words...

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Maybe?

cap: Your father was a stubborn old ox.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I was surprised when he died. Didn't think death had the patience.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: I'm glad you were with him. I wish to the Gods I had been.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: Did you make peace in the end?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: After 30 years of fighting, I don't think he remembered what started it.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: He asked me to stop calling myself Blackfish.

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: He said it was an old joke and it was never funny to begin with.

cap: I told him people had been calling me Blackfish for so long,

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: they don't remember my real name.

cap: I'd see him off.

cap: I wonder,

cap: I will never see them again.

cap: We don't know the truth. They could be in hiding.

cap: Robb believes they're alive.

cap: He's got to remain strong if he's to prevail.

cap: You're Robb Stark's wife.

cap: Hold still.

cap: Is it true what they say about him?

cap: I don't know. What do they say about him?

name: Walk of Punishment
cap: True.

cap: Martyn Lannister.

cap: Martyn Lannister.

cap: Unless it's a full moon.

cap: See? Nothing to fear.

cap: No men.

cap: Tormund. Climb the Wall.

cap: Take Orell and 20 good men. And take this one.

cap: He knows Castle Black's defences better than any of us.

cap: See if crows can fly.

cap: Believe me, girl, I want you there as soon as I can.

cap: Fight as a sellsword.

cap: I have friends there.

cap: Seven blessings to you.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: If I'm standing on it, it's my land.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: We were just watering the horses. We'll be on our way.

cap: Forgive my father.

cap: He was wounded fighting in the war.

cap: Our cottage burned down while he was gone, and my mother with it.

cap: He's never been the same.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: The Tullys of Riverrun.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: There's a storm coming.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: You'll be wanting a roof tonight.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: There's fresh hay in the barn.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: And Sally here makes rabbit stew just like her mom used to do.

name: Breaker of Chains
cap: We don't have much, but any man that bled for House Tully is welcome to it.

name: Breaker of Chains

name: Breaker of Chains
