cap: The noble Hizdahr zo Loraq can speak to me himself.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Queen Daenerys.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Tales of your beauty were not exaggerated.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I thank you.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Mine is one of the oldest and proudest families in Meereen.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Then it is my honour to receive you.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: My father,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: one of Meereen's most respected and beloved citizens,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: oversaw the restoration and maintenance of its greatest landmarks.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: This pyramid included.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: For that, he has my gratitude. I should be honoured to meet him.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You have, Your Grace.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You crucified him.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I pray you'll never live to see a member of your family treated so cruelly.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Your father crucified innocent children.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: My father spoke out against crucifying those children.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He decried it as a criminal act, but was overruled.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Is it justice to answer one crime with another?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I am sorry you no longer have a father,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: but my treatment of the masters was no crime.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You'd be wise to remember that.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What's done is done.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You are the queen and I am a servant of Meereen.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: A servant who does not wish to see its traditions eradicated.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And what traditions do you speak of? - Of funeral rite.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Proper burial in the Temple of the Graces.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: My father and 162 noble Meereenese are still nailed to those posts,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: carrion for vultures, rotting in the sun.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Your Grace, I ask that you order these men taken down

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: so that they might receive proper burials.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And what of the slave children these noble Meereenese crucified?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: They were rotting in the sun as well.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Would you have begged me for their right to a proper burial?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Your Grace, I cannot defend the actions of the masters.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I can only speak to you as a son who loved his father.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Let me take his body down.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Let me have him brought to the temple

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and buried with dignity so that he might find peace in the next world.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Bury your father, Hizdahr zo Loraq.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Thank you, my queen.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: How many more?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: There are 212 supplicants waiting, Your Grace.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Send the next one in.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: These meetings aren't always going to be this early, are they?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I was up late last night.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: So, does this mean I am a master of something now?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Coins, ships?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Lord Tywin and I already determined that

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I shall be the Master of Ships long before you...

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Lord Tywin, it's a great honour to have been granted a seat on this council. I...

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: The trial begins this afternoon.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: We only have the morning for affairs of state.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: So, shall we begin?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Sandor Clegane has been spotted in the Riverlands, my lord.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: A coward and a traitor.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: My birds tell me the Hound slaughtered five of our soldiers.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I believe the phrase 'fuck the king' was uttered.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Disgraceful.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What would it take to make the common soldier

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: stupid enough to try his luck with the Hound?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Ten silver stags seems a generous bounty.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Make it 100. What else?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: More whispers from the east, my lord.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: The Targaryen girl?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Daenerys has taken up residence in Meereen.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: She has conquered the city and rules as its queen.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Conquered with what?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: She commands an army of Unsullied, my queen.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Some 8,000 strong.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: She has a company of sellswords, the Second Sons.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: She has two knights advising her,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Jorah Mormont and Barristan Selmy.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And she has three dragons.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Baby dragons.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Larger every year, Your Grace.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Mormont is spying on her for us.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: No longer. He appears to be fully devoted to her.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: As for Ser Barristan,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: it would seem he took his dismissal from the Kingsguard a bit harder than anticipated.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He's an old man.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He wasn't fit to protect my son.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Joffrey didn't die on his watch.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Dismissing him was as insulting as it was stupid.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Don't tell me you're worried about a child halfway across the world.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: A child with two seasoned warriors counselling her

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and a powerful army at her back, Your Grace.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Lord Varys is right.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I have been to Essos and seen the Unsullied firsthand.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: They are very impressive on the battlefield.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Less so in the bedroom.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Dragons haven't won a war in 300 years.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Armies win them all the time.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: She must be dealt with.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: How, my lord? By force?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Eventually, if it comes to that.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Can your little birds find their way into Meereen?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Most certainly, my Lord Hand.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Mmm. Lord Tyrell, be a good man. Fetch my quill and paper.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Prince Oberyn.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Lord Varys.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Only Varys. I'm not actually a nobleman.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: No one is under obligation to call me lord.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And yet everyone does.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You seem quite knowledgeable about the Unsullied.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Did you spend much time in Essos?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Five years.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: May I ask why?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'Tis a big and beautiful world.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Most of us live and die in the same corner where we were born

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and never get to see any of it.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I don't want to be most of us.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Most of us aren't princes.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You are from Essos.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Where? Lys?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I have an ear for accents.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I've lost my accent entirely.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I have an ear for that as well.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Hmm.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: How did you get here?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: It's a long story.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: One you don't like telling people.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: People I trust.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: My paramour Ellaria, she would find you very interesting.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You should come to the brothel and meet her.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: We brought our own wine, not the swill they serve here.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: We have some lovely boys on retainer, but...

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You did like boys before?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Really?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Girls? Hmm.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I hope you won't be offended when I say I never would have guessed.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Not at all.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: But I was never interested in girls, either.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What then? - Nothing.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Everybody is interested in something.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Not me.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: When I see what desire does to people, what it's done to this country,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I am very glad to have no part in it.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Besides, the absence of desire

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: leaves one free to pursue other things.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Such as?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Let me guess, I've been pardoned.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Really?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Father's orders.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Well, we mustn't disappoint Father.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Kingslayer!

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I, Tommen of the House Baratheon,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: First of my Name,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: King of the Andals and the First Men,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and Lord of the Seven Kingdoms,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: do hereby recuse myself from this trial.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Tywin of the House Lannister, Hand of the King, Protector of the Realm,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: will sit as judge in my stead.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And with him Prince Oberyn of the House Martell

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and Lord Mace of the House Tyrell.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And if found guilty,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: may the gods punish the accused.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Tyrion of the House Lannister,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: you stand accused by the Queen Regent of regicide.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Did you kill King Joffrey?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: No.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Did your wife, the Lady Sansa?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Not that I know of.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: How would you say he died, then?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Choked on his pigeon pie.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: So you would blame the bakers?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Or the pigeons. Just leave me out of it.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: The crown may call its first witness.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Once we'd got King Joffrey safely away from the mob,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: the Imp rounded on him.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He slapped the king across the face

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and called him a vicious idiot and a fool.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: It wasn't the first time the Imp threatened Joffrey.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Right here in this throne room,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: he marched up those steps and called our king a halfwit.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Compared His Grace to the Mad King and suggested he'd meet the same fate.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And when I spoke in the king's defence,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: he threatened to have me killed.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Oh, why don't you tell them what Joffrey was doing?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Silence. - Pointing a loaded crossbow at Sansa Stark

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: while you tore at her clothes and beat her.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Silence!

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You will not speak unless called upon.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You're dismissed, Ser Meryn.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'Basilisk venom,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'widow's blood,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'wolfsbane,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'sweetsleep,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'tears of Lys,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'demon's dance...'

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: '...blindeye...'

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I think you have made your point, Grand Maester.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You have a lot of poison in your store.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Had, Prince Oberyn.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: My stores were plundered.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: By whom?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: By the accused, Tyrion Lannister, after he had me wrongfully imprisoned.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Grand Maester,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: you examined King Joffrey's corpse.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Was it without question poison that killed him?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Without question.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: This was found on the body of Dontos Hollard, the king's fool.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He was last seen spiriting Sansa Stark, the wife of the accused,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: away from the feast.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: She wore this necklace the day of the wedding.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Residue of the most rare and terrible poison

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: was found inside.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Was this one of the poisons stolen from your store?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: It was. The strangler.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: A poison few in the Seven Kingdoms possess.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And used to strike down the most noble child

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: the gods ever put on this good earth.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: CERSEl: 'I will hurt you for this.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'A day will come when you think you are safe and happy

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'and your joy will turn to ashes in your mouth

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'and you will know the debt is paid.'

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Your own brother said this to you?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Shortly before the Battle of Blackwater Bay.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I confronted him about his plans to put Joffrey on the front lines.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: As it turned out, when the attack came, Joff insisted on remaining at the battlements.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He believed his presence would inspire the troops.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Tyrion said,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'And you will know the debt is paid.'

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What debt?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I discovered he'd been keeping whores in the Tower of the Hand.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I asked him to confine his salacious acts

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: to the brothel where such behaviour belongs.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He wasn't pleased.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Thank you, Your Grace, for the courage of your testimony.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Do you remember the precise nature of this threat?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I'm afraid I do, my lord.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He said, 'Perhaps you should speak more softly to me, then.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'Monsters are dangerous

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'and just now kings are dying like flies.'

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And he said this to you at a meeting of the Small Council?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Yes.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: After we received word of Robb Stark's death.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He didn't seem gladdened by the news.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Perhaps his marriage to Sansa Stark

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: had made him more sympathetic to the northern cause.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You're excused, Lord Varys.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Father, may I ask the witness one question?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: One.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You once said

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: that without me, this city would have faced certain defeat.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You said the histories would never mention me,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: but you would not forget.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Have you forgotten, Lord Varys?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Sadly, my lord,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I never forget a thing.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: We will adjourn for now.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Toll the bells in an hour's time.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Clear the court!

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You'd condemn your own son to death?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I've condemned no one. The trial is not over.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: This isn't a trial. It's a farce.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Cersei has manipulated everything and you know it.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I know nothing of the sort.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You've always hated Tyrion. - He killed his king.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: As did I.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Do you know the last order the Mad King gave me?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: To bring him your head.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I saved your life so you could murder my brother?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: It won't be murder. It'll be justice. - Justice?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I'm performing my sworn duty as Hand of the King.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: If Tyrion is found guilty, he will be punished accordingly.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He'll be executed. - No, he'll be punished accordingly.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Once you said, 'Family is what lives on.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: 'All that lives on.'

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You told me about a dynasty that would last 1,000 years.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What happens to your dynasty when Tyrion dies?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I'm a Kingsguard, forbidden by oath to carry on the family line.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I'm well aware.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What happens to your name?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Your nephews?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Lancel Lannister?

cap: Others whose names I don't even remember?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What happens to my dynasty if I spare the life of my grandson's killer?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: It survives through me.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I'll leave the Kingsguard.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I'll take my place as your son and heir

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: if you let Tyrion live.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Done.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: When the testimony's concluded and a guilty verdict rendered,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Tyrion will be given the chance to speak.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He'll plead for mercy. I'll allow him to join the Night's Watch.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: In three days' time, he'll depart for Castle Black

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and live out his days at the Wall.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You'll remove your white cloak immediately.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You will leave King's Landing

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: to assume your rightful place at Casterly Rock.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You will marry a suitable woman

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: and father children named Lannister.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And you'll never turn your back on your family again.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You have my word.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: And you have mine.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Not going well, is it?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: You're going to be found guilty.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Oh, you think so? - And when you are,

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: you need to enter a formal plea for mercy and ask to be sent to the Wall.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Father's agreed to it.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He'll spare your life and allow you to join the Night's Watch.

cap: Ned Stark was promised the same thing and we both know how that turned out.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Father is not Joffrey. He'll keep his word.

cap: How do you know?

cap: Do you trust me?

cap: Keep your mouth shut. No more outbursts.

cap: This will all be over soon.

cap: The crown may call its next witness.

cap: State your name.

cap: Shae.

cap: Do you swear by all the gods that your testimony will be true and honest?

cap: I swear it.

cap: Do you know this man?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Yes. Tyrion Lannister.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: How do you know him?

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I was handmaiden to his wife Lady Sansa.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: This man stands accused of murdering King Joffrey.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: What do you know of this?

cap: I know that he's guilty.

cap: He and Sansa planned it together.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Silence!

cap: Continue.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: She wanted revenge for her father, her mother, her brother.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: Tyrion was happy to help.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He hated Joffrey. He hated the queen.

cap: He hated you, my lord.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: He stole poison from the Grand Maester's chamber

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: to put in Joffrey's wine.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men

cap: Why would he reveal such plans to his wife's maid?

cap: I beg your pardon?

cap: His whore.

cap: How did you come to be in his service?

cap: He stole me.

name: The Laws of Gods and Men
cap: I was with another man, a knight in your lordship's army.

cap: Silence!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I did.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And your wife has every right to criticize.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We can't allow fanatics to arrest the queen's brother

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: no matter his perversions.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Then...

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: can I tell Margaery you'll have Ser Loras released?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I told you, I'm not holding Ser Loras.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're the king.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I'm sure if you speak to the High Sparrow,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: he'll release the poor boy.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Halt!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: His Holiness is praying. He will not be disturbed.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Give the order and we'll clear out this rabble.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You mean, kill them?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Here at the sept?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You'd be sending them to meet the gods that they love.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Bastard!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're an abomination!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Born of sin!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Filthy bastard!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We'll find another way.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Abomination!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: My queen?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: There was no way to free Ser Loras without violence.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're the King of the Andals,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: the Lord of the Seven Kingdoms,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: the Protector of the Realm,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and you let a band of fanatics imprison your brother by law.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I'm going to speak with the High Sparrow.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Are you? When?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I-I don't know. - You don't know?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He was praying just now.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I have to send word to Grandmother.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Will you come back later?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I need to be with my family, Your Grace.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Of course.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You think highly of this boy?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Good.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Lord Commander of the Night's Watch.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And a bastard by some tavern slut.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Perhaps, but that wasn't Ned Stark's way.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I should have given you a son.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Not your fault.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Whose, then?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I gave you nothing but weakness.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And deformity.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Those scars mean nothing to the Lord of Light.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: My lady.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Her father is the Lord's chosen king,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and her father's blood runs through her veins.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You march on Winterfell soon?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We must to beat the snows.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Once before, you put your faith in Ser Davos

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and left me behind.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I hope you won't make that mistake again.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I won't.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I need you.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You only need faith, my king.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And you, my lady, what do you need?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: To serve my Lord.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Lord Ashford.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Lady Caulfield.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Oh, Lord Smallwood.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I've never even heard of these people.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: They haven't heard of you, either.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But we need men and they have some.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How many men does this Lord Mayzen have to send us?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: More than Lord Wibberley.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Not him. - I know, I'm sorry.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But we need men and supplies

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and Roose Bolton's the Warden of the North.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He murdered my brother.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We swore to be the watchers on the Wall.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We can't watch the Wall with 50 men.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And we can't get more men

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: without help from the Warden of the North.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Apologies, my lady.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Lord Commander.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How can I help you?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Come with us when we ride south.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: None of us know the castle as well as you do.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Its hidden tunnels, its weaknesses,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: its people.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Winterfell was your home once.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Don't you want to chase the rats out of it?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Castle Black is my home now.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: The Night's Watch take no part in the wars of the Seven Kingdoms.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: There's only one war.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Life against death.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Come, let me show you what you're fighting for.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're gonna show me some vision in the fire?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Forgive me, my lady, I don't trust in visions.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: No visions. No magic.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Just life.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Do you feel my heart beating?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: There's power in you.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You resist it, and that's your mistake.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Embrace it.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: The Lord of Light made us male and female.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Two parts of a greater whole.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: In our joining, there's power.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Power to make life,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: power to make light,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and power to cast shadows.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I don't think Stannis would like that very much.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Then we shouldn't tell him.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I can't. - Why?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I swore a vow.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I loved another.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: The dead don't need lovers.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Only the living.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I know.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But I still love her.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You know nothing, Jon Snow.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Are you lonely?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Just bored.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: My father used to tell me that boredom

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: indicates a lack of inner resources.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Were you bored a lot, too?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I know Castle Black

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: is no place for a child, but--

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I like it. I thought I'd be left at home.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I know Mother didn't want to bring me.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Why do you say that?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: She told me, 'I don't want to bring you.'

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: She shouldn't have said that.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Are you ashamed of me, Father?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: When you were an infant,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: a Dornish trader landed on Dragonstone.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: His goods were junk except for one wooden doll.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He had even sewn a dress on it in the colors of our house.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: No doubt he had heard of your birth

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and assumed new fathers were easy targets.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I still remember how you smiled when I put that doll in your cradle.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How you pressed it to your cheek.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: By the time we burned the doll, it was too late.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I was told you would die.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Or worse,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: the greyscale would go slow.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Let you grow just enough to know the world

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: before taking it away from you.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Everyone advised me to send you to the ruins of Valyria

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: to live out your short life with the Stone Men

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: before the sickness spread through the castle.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I told them all to go to hell.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I called in every maester on this side of the world.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Every healer. Every apothecary.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: They stopped the disease and saved your life.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: 'Cause you did not belong across the world

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: with the bloody Stone Men.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You are the Princess Shireen of House Baratheon.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And you are my daughter.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I thought I might find you here.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Your Aunt Lyanna.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Father never talked about her.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Sometimes I'd find him down here lighting the candles.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: They say she was beautiful.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I saw her once.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I was a boy living with your mother's family.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Lord Whent held a great tourney at Harrenhal.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Everyone was there.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: The Mad King, your father,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Robert Baratheon,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and Lyanna.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: She was already promised to Robert.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You can imagine what it was like for me,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: a boy from nowhere with nothing to his name,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: watching these legendary men

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: tilting at the lists.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: The last two riders were Barristan Selmy

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and Rhaegar Targaryen.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: When Rhaegar won, everyone cheered for their prince.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I remember the girls laughing when he took off his helmet

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and they saw that silver hair.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How handsome he was.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Until he rode right past his wife,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Elia Martell,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and all the smiles died.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I've never seen so many people so quiet.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He rode past his wife

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and he lay a crown of winter roses in Lyanna's lap.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Blue as frost.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How many tens of thousands had to die

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: because Rhaegar chose your aunt?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Yes, he chose her.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And then he kidnapped her and raped her.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Come.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Let's speak somewhere the dead can't hear us.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're dressed for riding.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I am.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Where are you going?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: King's Landing.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: King's Landing?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Cersei sent for me.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We mustn't let her sniff out any trouble.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You can't leave me here.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I know how hard it is to live with people you despise.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Believe me.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But it won't be for long.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How do you know?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Stannis Baratheon garrisons at Castle Black.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He'll march south to King's Landing

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: before the winter snows block his way.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But first he has to take Winterfell.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You don't know that. - I do.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Once he liberates these lands from the Boltons,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: he'll rally your father's bannermen to his cause.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: With the North behind him,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Stannis can finally take the Iron Throne.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You think he'll defeat the Boltons?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He has a larger army.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He's the finest military commander in Westeros.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: A betting man would put his money on Stannis.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: As it happens, I am a betting man.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And if you're right?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Stannis takes Winterfell,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: he rescues you from the most despised family in the North.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Grateful for your late father's courageous support of his claim,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: he names you Wardeness of the North.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But I--

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I wouldn't--

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Wardeness of the North?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You are the last surviving Stark.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He needs you.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And what if you're wrong?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: What if Stannis never attacks Winterfell?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Or he does and the Boltons defeat him?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Then you will take this Bolton boy, Ramsay,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and make him yours.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I don't know how to do that.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Of course you do.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He's already fallen for you.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: His father frightens me.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He should. He's a dangerous man.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But even the most dangerous men can be outmaneuvered.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And you've learned to maneuver from the very best.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I'll return before too long.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You'll be strong without me.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: The North will be yours.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Do you believe me?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I expect I'll be a married woman by the time you return.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Breakfast.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: That would have been a shit way to die.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: As far as I've seen, they're all shit ways to die.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Aye, but your lot have to give the singers a good ending.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I don't care what's sung about me when I'm dead.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: No?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Two knights off to rescue a princess.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Sounds like a good song to me.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Sounds like all the rest.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: What about you?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: What shit way would you choose?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: In my own keep drinking my own wine

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: watching my sons grovel for my fortune.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How disappointing.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I thought you'd have something more exciting planned.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I've had an exciting life.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I want my death to be boring.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How do you want to go?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: In the arms of the woman I love.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: She want the same thing?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Let's go.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: The captain of that ship--

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: what was he, Braavosi?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Pentoshi.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And he's headed to Oldtown?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: As I said. Why?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: What's to stop him from docking down the coast

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and telling the locals that Jaime Lannister is in Dorne?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: A bag of gold.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I'm not sure you understand

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: how much people hate your family in this part of the world.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: It was a heavy bag.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And I bet he swore all kinds of oaths to get it.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: But you won't be around if he breaks 'em.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How many you count?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Four.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How many do you think you can take?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: One if he's slow.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Halt!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Over the hill.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Fucked in the ass.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Hyah!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Morning, lads.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Glad we found you.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Who are you?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Cooper.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: This is Darnell.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're from King's Landing.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Accent gave me away?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Flea Bottom, whelped and whipped.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Why are you here?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Our ship capsized in the night.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We managed to swim ashore.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: It was a near thing, really.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Thought the sharks would get us.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: There are no sharks in Dorne.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Could have sworn those were shark fins.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Dolphins, maybe.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Throw your swords in the sand.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Boys, there's no need for this.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Just point us in the right direction,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: we'll find our way home.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Swords in the sand now.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Hyah! Hyah!

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: That one should be slow enough.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Nice move.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Luck.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You had a wonderful teacher.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Always wanted a Dornish stallion.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Beasts can run a day and night without tiring.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We'll ride to the Water Gardens

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: with a nice breeze in our faces.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: First we need to bury these bodies.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Birds have to eat, too.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Corpses raise questions. Questions raise armies.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We're not here to start a war.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Do you know how long it'll take us to dig all those holes?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I can't dig very well with one hand.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Not at all, really.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Mama.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Nym, Obara.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Will it be war?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Prince Doran will weep for your father, but nothing else.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We must avenge Oberyn ourselves.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Without Doran, we have no army to march against the Lannisters.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We don't need an army to start a war.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Queen Cersei loves her children.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And we have one of them.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You may have a problem.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: A ship's captain who found me in Planky Town

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: claiming he had information to sell.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He told me he smuggled Jaime Lannister into Dorne.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: He's come for Myrcella.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: If he gets to her before we do,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: we lose our only chance for revenge.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You must choose.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Doran's way and peace,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: or my way and war.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I'm with you always.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Nym?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Obara?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: When I was a child, Oberyn came to take me to court.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I had never seen this man,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and yet he called himself my father.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: My mother wept,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: said I was too young and a girl.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Oberyn tossed his spear at my feet and said,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: 'Girl or boy, we fight our battles,

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: but the gods let us choose our weapons.'

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: My father pointed to the spear

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: and then to my mother's tears.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I made my choice long ago.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Will you untie me?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Will you please untie me?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Will you please?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Thank you.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Who are you?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Your captor.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Do you have wine?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: No.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Can't sleep without wine.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Then stay awake.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're going the wrong way.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: My sister is in Westeros.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Westeros is west.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: We're heading east.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I'm not taking you to your sister.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You said you were taking me to the queen.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I am. Queen Daenerys Targaryen.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: She's the queen I serve.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: What a waste of a good kidnapping.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: It so happens I was heading there myself.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: What business would you have with the queen?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Gold and glory. Oh, and hate.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: If you'd ever met my sister, you'd understand.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: So, now that it's clear we are on the same side...

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: A highborn knight from the North of Westeros

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: down on his luck in Essos.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Dragon epaulets, bear sigil breastplate.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You're Jorah Mormont.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I have to ask.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: How exactly were you serving your queen

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: in a whorehouse half a world away?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Is it possible that you were running?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Why would you be running?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: And why would she have sent you away?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: Oh, wait.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: You were spying on her, weren't you?

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: It's all coming back to me.

name: Sons of the Harpy
cap: I was drunk through most of the small council meetings,

name: Sons of the Harpy

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Her father was Eddard Stark.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Her mother was Catelyn Stark.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: She had one sister, Sansa,

name: Oathbreaker
cap: and four brothers.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Three brothers.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Robb, Bran, Rickon.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: And a half-brother Jon.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: And where are they now?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: They may be dead for all a girl knows.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Tell me about the Hound.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Also dead.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Arya Stark left him to die. He was on her list.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: He was not on her list anymore.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: She had taken him off it.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Why? Didn't she want him dead any longer?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: She did and she did not.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: She sounds confused.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Yes, she was.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Who else was on Arya Stark's funny little list?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Cersei Lannister.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Gregor Clegane.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Walder Frey.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: That's a short list.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: That can't be everyone you want to kill.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Are you sure you're not forgetting someone?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Which name would you like a girl to speak?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: If a girl tells me her name,

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I will give her eyes back.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: A girl has no name.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Come.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: If a girl is truly no one,

name: Oathbreaker
cap: she has nothing to fear.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Who are you?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: No one.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: The Umbers are a famously loyal house.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Famously loyal to the Starks.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: And you, Lord Karstark.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Your people share blood with the Starks, don't they?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: But here we are. Times change.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: When my father became Warden of the North,

name: Oathbreaker
cap: your house refused to pledge their banners.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Your father was a cunt.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: My beloved father, the Warden--

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Your father was a cunt and that's why you killed him.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I might have done the same to my father

name: Oathbreaker
cap: if he hadn't have done me the favor of dying on his own.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: My father was poisoned by our enemies.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Mmm.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Why have you come to Winterfell, Lord Umber?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: The bastard Jon Snow led an army of wildlings past the Wall.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: We're farther north than any of you fuckers.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Wildlings come down, we always have to fight them first.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I like fighting wildlings. Been doing it all my life.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: But there are too many of them for us to beat back alone.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: So now you've come seeking help?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: We need to help each other.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: The colder it gets, the farther south those goat fuckers will roam.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Won't take them long to get here.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: You think a horde of wildlings can take Winterfell?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: If they get Jon Snow leading them, maybe.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: He knows this place better than we ever will.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Pledge your banners to House Bolton.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Swear loyalty to me as Warden of the North

name: Oathbreaker
cap: and we will fight together to destroy the bastard

name: Oathbreaker
cap: and all his wildling friends.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I'm not kissing your fucking hand.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Traditionally a bannerman kneels before his lord.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I'm not doing that either.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Why would I trust a man who won't honor tradition?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Your father honored tradition.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Knelt for Robb Stark.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Called him King of the North.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Was Robb Stark right to trust your father?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Then it appears we're at a bit of an impasse.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Fuck kneeling and fuck oaths.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I've got a gift for you.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: A girl, I hope. I prefer redheads.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: A girl, aye.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: A wild one.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I like them wild.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: And the boy, nice and young.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: The way Karstark likes them.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Who's this?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Rickon Stark.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: How do I know that's Rickon Stark?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Welcome home, Lord Stark.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: It's time.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: If you have any last words, now is the time.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: You shouldn't be alive.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: It's not right.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Neither was killing me.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: My mother's still living at White Harbor.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Could you write her?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Tell her I died fighting the wildlings.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I had a choice, Lord Commander.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Betray you or betray the Night's Watch.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: You brought an army of wildlings into our lands.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: An army of murderers and raiders.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: If I had to do it all over knowing where I'd end up,

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I pray I'd make the right choice again.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I'm sure you would, Ser Alliser.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: I fought, I lost.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Now I rest.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: But you, Lord Snow,

name: Oathbreaker
cap: you'll be fighting their battles forever.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: We should burn the bodies.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: You should.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: What do you want me to do with this?

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Wear it.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Burn it.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Whatever you want.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: You have Castle Black.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: My watch is ended.

name: Oathbreaker
cap: Fidel33 May 9, 2016

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Where you gonna go?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: South.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: What are you gonna do?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Get warm.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I was with you at Hardhome.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We saw what's out there.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We know it's coming here.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: How can you leave us now?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I did everything I could. You know that.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You swore a vow.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Aye, I pledged my life to the Night's Watch.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I gave my life. - For all nights to come.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They killed me, Edd! My own brothers.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You want me to stay here after that?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Riders approaching!

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Open the gate!

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: This is good soup.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Do you remember those kidney pies Old Nan used to make?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: With the peas and onions? - Mmm.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We never should have left Winterfell.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Don't you wish we could go back to the day we left?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I want to scream at myself, 'Don't go, you idiot.'

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: How could we know?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I spent a lot of time thinking about what an ass I was to you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I wish I could change everything.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We were children.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I was awful, just admit it.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You were occasionally awful.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I'm sure I can't have been great fun.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Always sulking in the corner while the rest of you played.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Can you forgive me? - There's nothing to forgive.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Forgive me. - All right.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: All right, I forgive you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You'd think after thousands of years,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: the Night's Watch would have learned how to make a good ale.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Where will you go?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Where will we go?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: If I don't watch over you,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Father's ghost will come back and murder me.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Where will we go?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I can't stay here, not after what happened.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: There's only one place we can go.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Home.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Should we tell the Boltons to pack up and leave?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We'll take it back from them.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I don't have an army.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: How many wildlings did you save?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They didn't come here to serve me.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They owe you their lives.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You think they'll be safe here if Roose Bolton remains Warden of the North?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Sansa. - Winterfell is our home.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: It's ours and Arya's and Bran's and Rickon's.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Wherever they are, it belongs to our family.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We have to fight for it.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I'm tired of fighting.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: It's all I've done since I left home.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I've killed brothers of the Night's Watch.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I've killed wildlings. I've killed men that I admire.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I hanged a boy younger than Bran.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I fought and I lost.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: If we don't take back the North, we'll never be safe.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I want you to help me.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: But I'll do it myself if I have to.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: My lady.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Ser Davos.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Will you stay here at Castle Black?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I will do as Jon Snow commands.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You serve Jon Snow now?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: He's the prince that was promised.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Forgive me, my lady, I thought that was Stannis.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: What happened down there?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: There was a battle. Stannis was defeated.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And Shireen?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: What happened to the princess?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I saw what happened.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I saw Stannis' forces defeated in the field.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: My lady, I'm Ser Davos Seaworth.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We've met before.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I was Kingsguard to Renly Baratheon.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Before Renly was assassinated with bloodmagic.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: That's in the past now.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Yes, it's in the past.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: It doesn't mean I forget.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Or forgive.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: He admitted it, you know.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Who did?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Stannis.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Just before I executed him.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: The Defender of the Vale!

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Uncle Petyr!

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: My lord.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Come and see.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I missed your name day. Go on.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: A falcon!

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: A gyrfalcon.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: The greatest and rarest of birds.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Last time I saw you, Baelish,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: you told me you were taking Sansa Stark home with you to the Fingers.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Indeed I was.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And yet not long ago, we received reports

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: that she has been married to Ramsay Bolton in Winterfell.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: On our way to the Fingers,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: we were set upon by a large force of Bolton men.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Seemed to know exactly when

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: we were traveling and exactly whom we were transporting.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Do you take me for a fool?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Tell me, Lord Royce,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: how many people knew of my travel plans with Sansa Stark?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I shared my intentions with you

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: and no one else.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Slander a man in his own home,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: you might find yourself crossing swords with him.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Your home is the Vale. The Lord of the Vale stands before us.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And only his judgment concerns me.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Shall we throw him through the Moon Door?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: My lord.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: My lord, I have always been faithful to House Arryn.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: To your father, to your mother, and now to you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Do you believe him, Uncle Petyr?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Lord Royce has served the Vale well.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: He's enjoyed a distinguished military career.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: If we could trust his absolute loyalty,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: he would make a capable commander in the wars to come.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You can trust my absolute loyalty, my lord.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I think he deserves one more chance. What do you say?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Fine.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I bring good news.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: My friends in the North tell me Sansa has escaped Winterfell.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I expect she's headed to Castle Black

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: where her brother serves as Lord Commander.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: But she won't be safe there, not with the Boltons after her.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: She's my cousin.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We should help her.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: That was my instinct as well.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Our lord has spoken.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Gather the Knights of the Vale.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: The time has come to join the fray.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You invite the enemy into our city?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I did.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: As a clever man once told me,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: 'We make peace with our enemies, not our friends.'

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I don't make peace with the queen's enemies.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I kill the queen's enemies.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Yes, that's the military approach.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And how has that worked here in Meereen?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I represent the diplomatic approach.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Our queen tried to make peace with the Masters

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: and they tried to murder her.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We enter these negotiations with open eyes.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Trust me. My own recent experience with slavery

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: has taught me the horrors of that institution.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: How many days were you a slave?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Long enough to know.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Not long enough to understand.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I bought this dwarf for a single gold honor.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And somehow you've risen

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: to the top of the Great Pyramid of Meereen.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: It's most impressive.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And now you speak for the Good Masters of Astapor.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Here's to reversals of fortune.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We came here to meet the queen

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: and instead we're greeted by a dwarf and a eunuch.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Let's make this simple, shall we? Tell me what you want.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We want you to leave Slaver's Bay.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Take your dragons and your mercenaries and go.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Queen Daenerys won't stay in Meereen forever.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Her path takes her westward.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: When we last met, I offered her ships

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: so she could return to Westeros where she belongs. She refused them.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: She refused them because hundreds of thousands

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: of men, women, and children still lived in chains.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: As they have since the dawn of time.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Not anymore. - You think you're a free man now?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You still follow orders.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Just because your master has silver hair and tits

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: doesn't mean she's not a master.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Friends, friends, friends, please.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: There have always been

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: those with wealth and power and those with nothing.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: That is the way of the world.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I'm not here to change the way of the world.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Slavery is the way of our world.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You don't need slaves to make money.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: There haven't been slaves in Westeros for hundreds of years

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: and I grew up richer than any of you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: But our queen recognizes that she erred

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: by abolishing slavery

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: without providing a new system to replace it.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: So here is the queen's proposal.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Slavery will never return to Meereen,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: but she will give the other cities of Slaver's Bay

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: time to adjust to the new order.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: What does that mean?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Instead of abolishing slavery overnight,

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: we will give you seven years to end the practice.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Slaveholders will be compensated

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: for their losses, of course, at fair prices.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: In exchange, you will cut off

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: your support for the Sons of the Harpy.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We do not support the Sons of the Harpy.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Fine, fine, but you will cut it off all the same.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I do hope you accept, my friends.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You will not receive a better offer.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Let us sail on the tide of freedom

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: instead of being drowned by it.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And as a parting gift to our honored guests...

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Give freedom a chance.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: See if it doesn't taste every bit as good as what came before.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Perhaps I should translate for you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We speak the Common Tongue.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Excellent. - You met with the slavers today.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I did.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Our brothers and sisters died fighting this scum.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Now you invite them to our city and drink wine with them.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I imagine this room was built

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: so the rulers could intimidate the ruled.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: But I am not your ruler.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I'm not the Breaker of Chains.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I'm not the Unburnt.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And I am certainly not the Mother of Dragons.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You are a stranger here.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: So why do you represent Meereen in these talks with our enemies?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Because our queen chose me as her advisor.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Until she returns from her travels--

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: When does she return?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Soon. You have my word.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We don't know you. We don't trust you. We know Torgo Nudho.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We fight with him against the Masters. We trust him.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: And that is exactly why Grey Worm took part in these negotiations.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: As commander of the Unsullied, he knows how to defeat the slavers

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: and he knows when it is time to make peace.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You have made peace with the slavers?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We offered terms.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Do not use me for your lies. - Those men respect you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They respect me because they know who I am.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They know I am loyal. - As do I.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I am loyal to my queen, not you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: If you betray her work, you are my enemy.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I am not betraying her work. I am trying to save her city.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You promised the slavers they could keep slavery.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: For a short time.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Seven years is not a short time for a slave.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You're right.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Slavery is a horror that should be ended at once.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: War is a horror that should be ended at once.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I can't do both today.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You are wrong to trust these men.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I don't trust the Masters. I trust their self-interest.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They're trustworthy if they're convinced

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: that working with me is in their self-interest.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You don't know them. You don't understand them.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We are not human in their eyes.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They look at me and see a weapon.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They look at her and see a whore.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They look at me and they see a misshapen little beast.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Their contempt is their weakness.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They'll underestimate us every time and we will use that to our advantage.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You will not use them.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: They will use you. That is what they do.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You all right?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Why don't you sit and catch your breath?

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I'm fine.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: I don't think you could ride the dragon.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: 20 years ago, maybe.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: What? - Our queen.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: She's wild, you know. Don't let her size fool you.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: It's hard enough for me and I'm a young man.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: You, I don't think your heart could take it.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Must make you angry that our queen chose me.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: Makes me sad. You'll disappoint her before long.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: She'll move on. - We'll all disappoint her before long.

name: Book of the Stranger
cap: We need each other right now. After we're done needing each other--

name: Book of the Stranger

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: No one knows. No one but me.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Jon isn't really my father's son.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: He's the son of Rhaegar Targaryen and my aunt, Lyanna Stark.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: He was born in a tower in Dorne.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: His last name isn't really Snow,

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: it's Sand.

cap: It's not.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Dornish bastards are named Sand.

cap: At the Citadel, I transcribed a High Septon's diary.

cap: He annulled Rhaegar's marriage to Elia.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: He wed Rhaegar and Lyanna in a secret ceremony.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Are you certain?

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: It's what the High Septon wrote in his private diary.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: I don't know why he'd lie.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Is this something you can see?

name: The Dragon and the Wolf

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: I am hers and she is mine... - I am his and he is mine...

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: from this day until the end of my days.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Robert's Rebellion was built on a lie.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Rhaegar didn't kidnap my aunt or rape her.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: He loved her.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You have to protect him.

cap: Promise me, Ned.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: He's never been a bastard.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: He's the heir to the Iron Throne.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: He needs to know.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: We need to tell him.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Are you all right?

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: It's just strange.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: In his own horrible way, I believe he loved me.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You did the right thing.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You did it.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: I'm just the executioner.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You passed the sentence.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You're the Lady of Winterfell.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Does that bother you?

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: I was never going to be as good a lady as you.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: So I had to be something else.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: I never could have survived what you survived.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You would have.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You're the strongest person I know.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: I believe that's the nicest thing you've ever said to me.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: Well, don't get used to it.

name: The Dragon and the Wolf
cap: You're still very strange and annoying.
